title: Honda Africa Twin to launch by June 2017, here's what to expect from the Triumph Tiger rival - The Financial Express
text: Auto Gallery Honda Africa Twin to launch by June 2017, here’s what to expect from the Triumph Tiger rival Honda Africa Twin to launch by June 2017, here’s what to expect from the Triumph Tiger rival Honda Motorcycles and Scooter India (HMSI) is set to launch an adventure tourer in India, the Africa Twin, by June this year. It will be sold as a CKD (Completely Knock-Down) unit that should help the brand to keep the pricing aggressive so as to compete against other adventure tourers in India like the Triumph Tiger.
